    <h1>Euroleague Response to COVID-19</h1>
    <p>Due to the need to keep fans, participants and game staff safe during the COVID-19 global pandemic, Turkish Airlines EuroLeague teams will begin the 2020-21 season with restrictions on attendance at their games.</p>
    <br>
    <p>The restrictions depend on national and/or local health guidelines that all Euroleague Basketball clubs are committed to fulfilling in order to help ensure the safe environments required to ultimately defeat the coronavirus.</p>
